title: De'Longhi Air-Conditioning | PAC EX100 Silent
description:
De'Longhi presents Pinguino PAC EX100 Silent, its most advanced air-conditioning model for stylish and efficient air-conditioning. Pinguino PAC EX100 Silent is the first De'Longhi Pinguino in A++ energy efficiency class, the real feel technology delivers the optimal comfort and keeps it over time.

Click here for more information about De'Longhi Real feel Technology: https://youtu.be/D6Plh6Atlq8

For more information on the De'Longhi Air conditioning click here: http://goo.gl/tJiIKQ
